data.description: Fully remodeled home set in the tranquil adult Community of Sunbird. This corner-lot 2-bed, 2-bath residence epitomizes elegant living! You'll find an open layout displaying vaulted ceilings and rich vinyl plank flooring bathed in natural light. The kitchen is a modern marvel, with a cozy breakfast nook, quartz counters, chic white shaker cabinets, matching appliances, a walk-in pantry, and an inviting peninsula with a breakfast bar. Retreat through double doors to the main bedroom, a peaceful haven with a walk-in closet, plantation shutters, and a private bathroom. Discover a charming covered patio in the backyard, offering personal space for relaxation or entertainment under the vast Arizona sky. Take a look at all of the updates
